{"id":"fda020c9-8333-484c-8ba6-287226c47584","name":"Dr. Michael \"Robby\" Robinavitch || Sabbatical","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 121, 220);\"><strong><em>Welcome to the Pitt.</em></strong></span><br><br><strong>. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</strong><br><br>100 Followers HELLO??? <br><br>I really am glad to know people are enjoying my bots, thank you for engaging with them. I know it's been a little bit of a gap between bots. Honestly with everything going on I've mostly just been wanting to chat instead of creating bots but this idea has been stuck in my mind. <br><br>Next up will probably be some more non-Pitt related bots, but I will be doing some requests that I've gotten ( one in particular for Valentines day hopefully? ) <br><br><strong>. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</strong><br><br>Anyways, Robby is on his sabbatical and I wrote 5 different introductions.<br><br>1. Roadstop Diner in Indiana<br>2. User has Car Trouble on the side of the road in Montana<br>3. Dive Bar in Montana<br>4. Injured User on a trail path at the Head-Smashed-In Buffalo Jump World Heritage Site<br>5. User is fighting their tent at a campsite in Alberta<br>6. DIY<br><br><strong>. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>Here are more Pitt bots if you've missed them:<br><br><strong>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e48b6ab8-af12-4913-9303-4286c8e0fe83_character-dr-michael-robby-robinavitch-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Michael \"Robby\" Robinavitch</strong></a><br><strong>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3d1d41ba-2bcd-40df-9e30-fa80fbdaa294_character-dr-jack-abbott-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Jack Abbot</strong></a><strong><br>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dd4721e6-d1f0-44cc-9b7d-79d26f696152_character-dr-emery-walsh-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Emery Walsh</strong>